Package: simplePlotTable
Type: Package
Title: Easily Alignable Tables in ggplot2
Version: 1.0.0
Author: person("Daniel", "Schmitz", email="daniel.schmitz@igp.uu.se", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Daniel Schmitz <daniel.schmitz@igp.uu.se>
Description: Draws tables using ggplot2's text geom with minimal styling.
  This allows them to be easily aligned to other plots.
